    "body": "Sounds like the AI ran out of base space around the MCV. This has nothing to do with Lua.\n\nIn TS/RA2, there was a property for the AI, that if it cannot place the building in x amount of tries it abandons the production of that one. That should work a ton better compared to your idea, because yours have the danger of deadlocking the AI production queue for unnecessarily long times.\n"
