    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Oh look, we've got a badass over here!\n\nYou have better ideas? Doesn't seem so. Have you seen the TS/RA2 AI failing with buildings many times? Fun fact, WW set this to two, so the AI gives up after two tries... this worked pretty well even on yaps where the mapper didn't added water, but forgot to disable the shipyards...\n\nMy suggestion works on a game which never even had such issues.\n\nBut if we suck at coding and security, please, fix it yourself, teach us, you grandmaster, you must know it a lot better than us!\n"
