    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> Play mod RA on any large map and eventually the game freezes for 5 seconds every 3 seconds or so. With many debug messages similar to: AI (X) has nowhere to place apwr.\n\nThis is a duplicate of https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/4717. Closing.\n\n> Btw have you guys tried using LuaJIT?\n\nThe [Lua API](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/wiki/Lua-API) is only used for mission scripting, not AI although that is also an idea. https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/issues/4947\n"
